---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Why this blog exists: a public notebook for my own learning and memory."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-07-10')}
>
	<p>
		This blog is a public notebook. I write it mainly <strong>for myself</strong> — to keep
		learning and to remember. Writing things down forces me to understand them properly, and
		reading them back later reminds me where I've been. If anyone else finds these notes useful,
		that's a bonus, not the goal.
	</p>

	<p>It mixes life and technical content, organized by tags:</p>

	<ul>
		<li><strong>life</strong> — life in Japan (pregnancy, baby born)</li>
		<li><strong>japan</strong> — living in Japan</li>
		<li><strong>opensource</strong> — starting open source, and lessons learned from it</li>
		<li><strong>career</strong> — career records</li>
		<li><strong>tech</strong> — technical articles</li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		Posts are written in Traditional Chinese, English, or Japanese — one language per post,
		whichever fits the topic and my mood. Each post is tagged with its language.
	</p>
</Layout>
